latestPosts.caption:
You said that you are looking for yourself
but don’t know the path.
I said there are two 
either close your eyes & look into,
Or look into the eyes of others 
as they are mirrors to you.
You said the second path is better
as mirrors don’t lie
I said, “This is an illusion”
Have you not seen the letters in the mirror? 
They are always inserted in it,
So you may be disillusioned.
Close your eyes & look into,
Either you will lose yourself
Or you will find your self
In both cases you will
Either be nothing or, everything
&
you know,
Nothingness gives birth to everything.

॰ शून्य ॰
